title: Heeeeeeeeeeeeeeelp :(
body: open pc, league dissapear, re-install, press launch, nothing happens. Repair, scans 100 files, launch, nothing happens. Help me :C

replies.body: Its all good now, thanks for helping me out :D

I'm here to help!  At this point, your client should have patched to the updated version since the[ legacy retirement](http://euw.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/features/legacy-client-now-retired).  Since it hasn't yet and isn't launching, then a security setting might be blocking you from doing so.  Go over each step of the [permissions](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) guide to get this fixed up.  Let me know if you have any questions!
